<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 01:27:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3dd5609c35a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;#FensterFreitag&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An old, small, white wooden double window, in whose glass a very orange and partly pink sunrise is reflected. The trees appear as black silhouettes against the light. The picture was taken at 3 am" height="2127" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a3dd5609c35a.jpg" width="3104"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 01:27:00 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3dd297bf951</link><description>&lt;p&gt;它有眼睛！&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A bowl of ramen with a halved soft-boiled egg." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a3dd297bf951.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 01:15:07 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3dcb51d965a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Dipper 和 Patches 正在闯入灰/黑白色的猫咪派对。😸&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Screenshot from Neko Atsume 2 showing a bunch of gray and white or black and white cats hanging out on the toys, and two brown and white cats spoiling the theme" height="2868" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/jezlyn/6a3dcb51d965a.png" width="1320"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://jezlyn.some.pics"&gt;@jezlyn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jun 2026 00:44:04 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3dafbd384f5</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这幅位于道格拉斯剧院旁的壁画，由洛杉矶艺术家汉娜·韦布为2024年梅肯壁画节创作。作品描绘了一只栖息在马丁·路德·金停车楼上的大蓝鹭——这种鸟类原产于梅肯。从城市天际线一英里多外的地方都能清晰望见。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Colorful mural of a stylized heron on a parking garage wall. The geometric design and cool hues of blue and purple create a bold, artistic effect." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a3dafbd384f5.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 22:46:24 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>时隔一年重返图书馆</title><link>https://some.pics/6a3daf4fba884</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天去了图书馆，这是超过一年来第一次。以前我几乎每周都去，但不知怎么地，就没了这个习惯。我也不确定为什么。只是很高兴终于能再次前往。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='A hand holds the book "Sketchbook for the Artist" by Sarah Simblet, featuring a grey circle on the cover, against a backdrop of comic books on a library shelf.' height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a3daf4fba884.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 22:44:35 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>